y accrete gas, and the AGN\nfraction in low-mass galaxies have important implications for the build-up of\nthe entire BH and galaxy populations with time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Jan 2022 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2022 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-22"}
