g first\nprinciples from combinatorics/probability, ii.) by using Fourier analysis of\nBoolean functions. Finally, we analyze the accuracy of the private mechanism on\nvarious social choice functions. The results in this paper thereby help bridge\ntwo prominent fields of social choice theory and differential privacy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jan 2022 06:22:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-26"}
