 the HMM works as a energy selective coupler for multi-excitonic\nsystems as MoS$_2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jan 2022 07:07:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2022 04:47:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-05"}
