ve a multilinear De Leeuw restriction theorem for pairs\n$\\Gamma<G$ with $c(\\Gamma) = 1$. We also obtain multilinear versions of the\nlattice approximation theorem, the compactification theorem and the\nperiodization theorem. Consequently, we are able to provide the first examples\nof bilinear multipliers on nonabelian groups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jan 2022 15:42:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 05:47:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 19 Mar 2023 21:15:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-21"}
